doctype html
html(lang="en")
  head
    title Oscar | Smart, simple health insurance.
    link(rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="mystyles.css")
    button OSCAR
    button Login
    button Menu
  body
    h1 Hi, we're Oscar.
    h1 Smart, simple health insurance.
    button Get Your Quote
    button Watch the Video
    img(src="./images/DownArrow.png")

    h2 Better care, lower cost
    p We're revolutionizing health insurance through technology, data and design.

    form
      img(src="./images/BetterPlans.png")
      h2 Better Plans
      p.
        Choose from plans that are easy to understand, provide comprehensive coverage, and give you lots of free perks.
        Learn More

    form
      img(src="./images/BetterHealthcare.png")
      h2 Better Healthcare
      p.
        Access thousands of top-notch doctors in your area, talk to a doctor 24/7, and visit your primary care doctor for free.
        Learn More

    form
      img(src="./images/BetterExperience.png")
      h2 Better Experience
      p.
        Use our app or website to find the right doctors, manage prescriptions, and earn rewards for staying active.
        Learn More

    form
      h2 Modern technology for modern care
      p We're using technology to simplify the entire health insurance experience. You can use our app to talk to a doctor and get prescriptions without ever leaving home. Keep track of your health history with a timeline and earn rewards for staying active with a free Misfit step tracker.
      img(src="./images/ModernTechnology.png")

    form
      img(src="./images/OscarAlmost.png")
      h2 Oscar is for (almost) everyone
      p We currently offer plans to individuals, couples, and families living in parts of New York, New Jersey, California and Texas who don't already receive health insurance from an employer. If you're not in our area, stay tuned. We're expanding quickly.

    form
      h2 Help us make healthcare simple, smart, and friendly
      p As a team of engineers, designers, data scientists, healthcare experts and many more, we're on a mission to reinvent how care is delivered. Our goal is to have the happiest members paying the lowest costs for the healthiest outcomes.
      img(src="./images/HelpMake.png")

